{
  "stem": "7337.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He exchanged the daily takings of his stores into gold coins daily, except on shabbat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't think the stores were closed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And he came through that period of the inflation in Germany a very wealthy man.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He sold men's hats and caps, nothing else.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't really know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But somewhere around 60 or 70 stores.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I worked in a store every [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] free day that I had, I used to spend there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My job was to put the hat-- the sold hats into a paper bag.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember that very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He wasn't interested.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother lived a very spoiled life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] She was not a well woman from 1928 onwards, and needed a lot of care.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] She also came from a wealthy background, and she never had to work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She died of cancer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1934, in France.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "German.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it must be realized that in Germany, Jews were [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] different in look to the Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jews looked-- [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] well, the Jewish look was totally different to the Germanic look, which was the Aryan look, like the Swedes and the Norwegians and Danish people.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in-- one of the things that made Hitler's rise easy, as far as anti-Semitism was concerned, the Jews stood out in a crowd.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People knew you were a Jew by looking at you because you looked different.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is not the case in countries like France, or Spain, or any of the-- Italy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it was the case in Austria, and in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Absolutely.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would guess--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Perhaps 10%, 12% of the-- of the class.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not directly.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
